---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="pt-24 pb-12 bg-slate-950 border-t border-white/5 text-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-16 mb-20">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8 group cursor-default">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-transform">
            <span class="font-black text-white text-2xl">A</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter text-white">ANDAIME<span class="text-primary">PRO</span></span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-sm leading-relaxed mb-8 text-lg font-medium">
          A maior autoridade em locação de equipamentos para trabalho em altura. Segurança certificada e logística de elite para sua obra.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
           <a href="https://instagram.com" class="w-10 h-10 bg-white/5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-primary transition-all hover:scale-110 active:scale-95">
             <span class="sr-only">Instagram</span>
             <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zm0-2.163c-3.259 0-3.667.014-4.947.072-4.358.2-6.78 2.618-6.98 6.98-.059 1.281-.073 1.689-.073 4.948 0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98-1.281-.059-1.69-.073-4.949-.073zm0 5.838c-3.403 0-6.162 2.759-6.162 6.162s2.759 6.163 6.162 6.163 6.162-2.759 6.162-6.163c0-3.403-2.759-6.162-6.162-6.162zm0 10.162c-2.209 0-4-1.79-4-4 0-2.209 1.791-4 4-4s4 1.791 4 4c0 2.21-1.791 4-4 4zm6.406-11.845c-.796 0-1.441.645-1.441 1.44s.645 1.44 1.441 1.44c.795 0 1.439-.645 1.439-1.44s-.644-1.44-1.439-1.44z"/></svg>
           </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tighter uppercase">Navegação</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li><a href="/servicos" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-all flex items-center gap-2 group">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></span>
            Equipamentos
          </a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-all flex items-center gap-2 group">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></span>
            Segurança (Blog)
          </a></li>
          <li><a href="/contato" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-all flex items-center gap-2 group">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></span>
            Orçamentos
          </a></li>
          <li><a href="/sobre" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-all flex items-center gap-2 group">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></span>
            Sobre Nós
          </a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tighter uppercase">Contato</h4>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-400 font-medium">
          <p class="flex items-center gap-3">
             <span class="text-primary font-black">📞</span> (11) 3344-5566
          </p>
          <p class="flex items-center gap-3">
             <span class="text-primary font-black">📧</span> contato@andaimepro.com.br
          </p>
          <p class="mt-8 text-sm opacity-60 leading-relaxed">
            Av. Paulista, 1000 - Bela Vista<br/>
            São Paulo - SP
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-12 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-8 text-center md:text-left">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium">
        © {currentYear} <span class="text-white font-black">ANDAIME PRO</span>. Todos os direitos reservados.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-8">
        <a href="/privacidade" class="text-xs text-gray-500 hover:text-white uppercase tracking-widest font-black transition-colors">Privacidade</a>
        <a href="/termos" class="text-xs text-gray-500 hover:text-white uppercase tracking-widest font-black transition-colors">Termos de Uso</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

